---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/paths';
---

<BaseLayout title="Coaching" description="Beth Glick offers coaching for those called to draw outside the lines.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24">
    <!-- Hero image -->
    <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-200 mb-12">
      <img
        src={url("/images/hero/coaching-hero.jpg")}
        alt="Coaching"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I used to be fluent in the language of getting things done. I co-ran a global consulting firm, coached hundreds of organizational leaders, advised on how to invest millions of dollars, and helped design strategies to advance justice and systems change.
      </p>

      <p>
        And then something shifted. Not dramatically — more like a slow erosion. A flattening of joy. A growing distance between the work I was doing and what felt alive inside me. I began asking different questions. Not "how do we optimize?" but "what does it mean to thrive?" Not "what's the strategy?" but "what are we not seeing?"
      </p>

      <p>
        I stepped away from conventional success and stepped into uncertainty. Into inquiry. Into the kinds of experiences and questions that most professional spaces don't make room for.
      </p>

      <p>
        Now, through my PhD research in consciousness studies, I explore what it means to thrive differently. I study meditation, journeying, creativity, altered states — drawing from neuroscience, psychology, philosophy. I'm drawn to synchronicity, intuition, moments of awe. And I'm interested in what re-enchants us — and how to live in ways that are grounded in intuition and intellect, embodiment and imagination, presence and perspective.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Second image -->
    <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-stone-200 my-12">
      <img
        src={url("/images/hero/coaching-secondary.jpg")}
        alt="Coaching"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Coaching offering -->
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Interested in working together?</h2>

      <p>
        I offer coaching for those called to draw outside the lines. You might be at a pivotal point in your life—or simply curious about what lives beyond convention. Expect empathy, provocation, and experimentation. A space to try things on, shift your lens, and explore new ways of being.
      </p>

      <p>
        <a href="mailto:bethglick@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-stone-800 !text-white text-sm rounded-lg hover:bg-stone-700 transition-colors !no-underline">
          Reach out to schedule an exploratory conversation
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
